      • execute

        public void execute()
             throws gate.creole.ExecutionException
        This method runs the gazetteer. It parses the document and looks-up the parsed phrases from the maps, in which the phrases vs. annotations are set, in order to generate an annotation set. It assumes that all the needed parameters are set. If they are not, an exception will be fired.
        Specified by:
        execute in interface gate.Executable
        Overrides:
